ArrangeByScore(classlist){
 Arraylist<Group> G;
  for (int i=0, i<=G.size(),i++)
    G.get(i%G.size()).add(classlist.get(i));
    }

 This algorithm will calculate students' score as a order,when the score is sort ,using this algorithm will like 
          1 2 3
          4 5 6
          7 8 9   which 1 4 7 is a group. but I think this is not good~
          
          
          
